<h1>I want to stop drinking but my spouse drinks and keeps alcohol in the house</h1>
<p>Enlisting social support, including family support, is a key for successfully decreasing alcohol intake. Try announcing your goal of decreasing you’re drinking to your spouse and enlisting their support. Ask if your spouse will join you in making your home a “safe zone” where alcohol is not allowed.</p>
